OL,3,CHigh rates of violence, self-harm and
OL,4,Cabuse at women's prison, inspection
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FAn inspection of HMP Eastwood Park in
OL,8,FSouth Gloucestershire has found it had
OL,9,Fthe highest rate of assaults against
OL,10,Fstaff of all women's prisons in the
OL,11,Fcountry.
OL,13,FInspectors from His Majesty's
OL,14,FInspectorate of Prisons (HMIP) visited
OL,15,Fthe prison for two weeks in June and
OL,16,FJuly, for the first time since 2022.
OL,18,FAt the time of the inspection 360
OL,19,Fwomen were being held at the prison,
OL,20,Fwhich has a capacity of 415 spaces.
