OL,3,CHigh rates of violence, self-harm and
OL,4,Cabuse at women's prison, inspection
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThey found the rate of self-harm was
OL,8,F"extremely high", with too many "very
OL,9,Fmentally unwell women" sent there due
OL,10,Fto lack of community services like
OL,11,Fmental health hospitals.
OL,13,FIn the last 12 months, figures from
OL,14,Fthe HMIP found there were 1,493 new
OL,15,Farrivals to the prison, with 800 of
OL,16,Fthose women having a history of self-
OL,17,Fharm.
