OL,3,CHigh rates of violence, self-harm and
OL,4,Cabuse at women's prison, inspection
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FInspectors noted that staff "often
OL,8,Fused force" to prevent self-harm and
OL,9,Fmany of the assaults on staff occurred
OL,10,Fwhile inmates were being restrained
OL,11,Fand that prisoners were
OL,12,F"unnecessarily" locked in their cells
OL,13,Fat times.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the Ministry of
OL,16,FJustice, which runs the prison estate,
OL,17,Fsaid it takes the issues of self-harm
OL,18,Fand violence against staff "extremely
OL,19,Fseriously".
